This is Service for Postmaster module [https://objectivehtml.com/index.php] which serves a a bridge between Social Update module [http://devot-ee.com/add-ons/social-update] and Postmaster. It allows notifications to be posted to authorized social accounts.

The advantage of this bridge is that the notifications can be triggered not only when entry is posted, but when any event/hook supported by Postmaster is taking palce.

Following social networks are supported:
* Facebook
* Twitter
* LinkedIn

Social Update must be installed and social networks authorized before setting up notifications. 

Postmaster and Social Update modules are required.